// Instructions: Create a function that takes a number as an argument, increments the number by +1 and returns the result.


function addition(num) {
  return ++num;                 // or return number + 1; NOTE: use prefix vs. postfix; postfix returns argument before incrementing 1
  }     
  
addition(0) ➞ 1
addition(9) ➞ 10
addition(-3) ➞ -2
